title: Satkar Pure Vegetarian
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Chinese, Indian, Western, Delivery, Take-out
description: Pure vegetarian cafe/restaurant, with many vegan options. Good menu of Indian, some Chinese and some western items. Lots of sandwiches, milk shakes, ice cream and fruit juice options. Local atmosphere full of young couples, business people, families. There are 4 dining venue options: Indoor room with AC, indoor room with fans open to outside patios, patio seating and patio standing. Has take-away and home delivery menu.
